snippet: U.S. Vice President Joe Biden will go to Guatemala on Friday to meet Central American leaders about the influx of unaccompanied minors illegally entering the United States, senior administration officials said on Sunday....

headline.print_headline: Biden to Meet Central America Leaders About Child Migrant Wave
headline.main: Biden to Meet Central America Leaders About Child Migrant Wave

lead_paragraph: U.S. Vice President Joe Biden will go to Guatemala on Friday to meet Central American leaders about the influx of unaccompanied minors illegally entering the United States, senior administration officials said on Sunday.
